United States – This man in question stands a good chance of heading to jail for many years after impregnating a minor. Relationship adviser and blogger, Joro Olumofin has shared the story of a woman whose husband impregnated a minor in the United States of America and took her for abortion. There were complications and the girl is presently battling for her life. The man has been detained by the police and is set to be charged to court. This has prompted his wife to consider abandoning him because he had been cheating on her for long. Read her story below: Source